data.description: ** REDUCED FOR QUICK SALE DUE TO BUYERS LACK OF PREFORMANCE **  Exceptional Family Home with Unmatched Features in Palm Harbor Prepare to be captivated by this remarkable 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom family home located in the highly coveted Palm Harbor community. This property stands out with its unique qualities, thoughtfully designed features, and unparalleled value. If you're seeking the perfect blend of luxury and comfort, look no further. Prime Location: Situated in one of Palm Harbor's most desirable neighborhoods, this property offers serene suburban living while being just moments away from top-rated schools, shopping, dining, and the pristine Gulf Coast beaches. Elegance in Every Detail: From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open, airy living space adorned with elegant finishes and modern touches. The gourmet kitchen, stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, and an abundance of cabinetry. Master Suite Retreat: Your master bedroom is a sanctuary of tranquility with an en-suite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms provide versatility and comfort for family members or guests. Outdoor Paradise: Step into your private outdoor oasis, complete with a screened-in patio, perfect for enjoying meals, relaxing, or entertaining. The expansive backyard is a canvas awaiting your personal touch—create your own garden retreat or dream pool area. Upgraded Bathrooms: Both bathrooms have been thoughtfully updated with modern fixtures and high-end finishes, promising a spa-like experience. Two-Car Garage: Convenience meets security with the attached two-car garage, providing ample space for vehicles and storage. Neighborhood Amenities: A-rated schools within easy reach Abundant nearby parks, recreational areas, and nature trails Explore historic downtown Palm Harbor just minutes away Effortless commuting with quick access to major highways Additional Features: Newer roof and HVAC system Freshly painted interior Low HOA fees This property is a standout opportunity to own a slice of paradise in Palm Harbor. With its unmatched features, incredible location, and attractive pricing, it won't be available for long. Your dream home awaits!
